{"tid":1080564,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"再度被質疑「買榜」？MOMOLAND音樂節目獲一位引發爭議…各家粉絲不滿：無法接受！","createTime":"2019-03-27T16:30:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T04:48:44.000Z","uid":152432,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9d19adff03ce7aa11d73770a8fc8fe618536d739","tid":1080564,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"時隔多月MOMOLAND近期以迷你專輯《Show Me》回歸，主打歌〈I'm So Hot〉也是繼之前的洗腦夯曲〈BBoom BBoom〉、〈BAAM〉後再次與知名製作人「新沙洞老虎」合作<br />\n<br />\n而在3月26日的音樂節目《THE SHOW》中，MOMOLAND以11分之差險勝音源強盜MAMAMOO獲得一位，節目播出後，引起了許多粉絲們的不滿，提出數據質疑MOMOLAND「買榜」<br />\n<br />\n從計分上來看，MAMAMOO在第一項評分「音源+唱片」分數比MOMOLAND多出一千多分，第二項「MV瀏覽量+專業人員評分+事前投票」分數則是MOMOLAND以總分3740勝出，而這兩項也是最受爭議的部分<br />\n<br />\n另外第一項音源和唱片評分也被指出，在韓國具公信力的Melon、Genie等音樂周榜上，MAMAMOO的名次分別在1～12不等，MOMOLAND的名次則落在19～194不等，甚至在部分音樂榜上並未進榜<br />\n<br />\n專輯銷量方面MAMAMOO更是多出MOMOLAND約五倍，更加加深了MOMOLAND的「買榜」疑雲，令許多MAMAMOO和他家團體的粉絲表示無法接受"},{"pid":"8440c583dc4cd538d08f6d3ab3e47e5f49ea712e","tid":1080564,"uid":63057,"like":20,"dislike":6,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾mml, 應該everglow攞先<br />\n明明everglow youtube 同銷量都高過mml"},{"pid":"61580e2b020fbdb631f972ec740d9090bbc3ca18","tid":1080564,"uid":213300,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:42:21.000Z","msg":"mml狗出嚟解釋吓"},{"pid":"d5092879120ec6907a6d70167c39a8384487de3e","tid":1080564,"uid":136738,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"@nancy.yeji老公"},{"pid":"047885c9d267373b00d5f414b0048c112b679440","tid":1080564,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T16:44:34.000Z","msg":"補圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SKDKLCO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSKDKLCO.jpg&h=01b86e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mx64LCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmx64LCP.jpg&h=db766413&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi